# Lead-form email delivery — Google Workspace (Gmail SMTP), no third-party service.
#
# The route hardcodes host/port/user/to/from (smtp.gmail.com:465, jw@capitalwayne.com).
# The ONLY secret is the Gmail app password below.
#
# SETUP:
#   1. jw@capitalwayne.com must have 2-Step Verification ON.
#   2. Create an app password: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
#      (16 characters). Workspace admins may need to allow app passwords.
#   3. Add GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD in Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables
#      (Production). For local testing, also put it in .env.local.

GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=your-16-char-google-app-password
